Class ClassOptionWithListenerOption

java.lang.Object
com.github.javacliparser.AbstractOption
moa.options.AbstractClassOption
moa.options.ClassOption
moa.options.ClassOptionWithListenerOption
All Implemented Interfaces:
Option, Serializable
public class ClassOptionWithListenerOption
extends ClassOption
ClassOption that can be given a ChangeListener. The listener is notified whenever a new value is set for this option.
